data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning brick residence boasts timeless elegance and modern comfort. With 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a fenced in back yard and a new roof, this property offers the perfect blend of luxury and practicality for today's discerning homeowner. Spacious and sunlit, the four bedrooms provide ample space for your family and guests. With two master suites, complete with a spa-like en-suite bathroom and walk-in closets. The well-appointed bathrooms feature high-end finishes and fixtures, ensuring that every morning feels like a visit to a luxurious spa. The heart of the home is the open-concept living area, featuring a gourmet kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, breakfast nook, a generous dining space, and a cozy living room with a fireplace - perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. Step outside to your private oasis! The fenced yard is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, providing a safe and secure space for children and pets to play while you relax on the patio. The home's interior is adorned with exquisite finishes, including hardwood floors, crown molding, and custom cabinetry, showcasing a level of craftsmanship that sets this property apart. Your vehicles will be well protected in the spacious two-car garage, offering plenty of storage space for all your needs. This home has been meticulously maintained and is move-in ready, offering a perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. Whether you're enjoying a quiet evening by the fireplace, hosting a BBQ in the backyard, or taking a stroll through the friendly neighborhood, you'll quickly fall in love with the lifestyle this home offers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional brick home yours. Contact an agent today to schedule a showing!
